name: Aesthetic Decapitation
description: Designed by the ever-so-creative Craig Watkins Decapitation, bright beautiful colors, eyeballs, sweet patterns, little monsters, what else do you need to make an amazing shirt? Like all of our other shirts, printed on a smooth-as-a-baby's-bottom fitted American Apparel ringspun cotton tee. Guaranteed 100% sweatshop free. It's pretty much the best tshirt experience you will ever receive, short of going naked of course, but this way it's actually legal. Model wearing medium.

name: Pandemic Ignorance
description: Designed by the man with the plan, who put almost as much of himself into this brand as anyone else, the amazing Colin Gauntlett Whenever some punk kid comes stompin' through our turf, we gotta put up a little resistance, but what do we end up doing?
